name: Ubiquity
description:
This is what I have become, my dance has mutated, from being physical, to becoming one more product of these metarveses, it has been difficult but the process is very interesting, I like to discover the possibilities of playing with my body and technology, This is now my face that comes to say who I am, where I am going and why I need to travel and know.

This is a collaboration with DJ Luis Mora.
